
#################################
####    Account: Fastmail    ####
#################################

IMAPAccount     fastmail
Host            imap.fastmail.com
SSLType         IMAPS
SSLVersions     TLSv1.2
User            deper29@fastmail.fm
PassCmd         "secret-tool lookup fastmail imap"
AuthMechs       LOGIN

IMAPStore       fastmail-remote
Account         fastmail

MaildirStore    fastmail-local
Path            ~/Maildir/fastmail/
Inbox           ~/Maildir/fastmail/INBOX
Flatten         .

Channel         fastmail
Far             :fastmail-remote:
Near            :fastmail-local:
Patterns        "INBOX" "*"
Expunge         Both
SyncState       *
Sync            All
Create          Near
CopyArrivalDate Yes

